  "texts": [
    "A similarity threshold, θ = 0.7, is set to identify potential duplicates.",
    "A new skill is considered redundant and excluded from the library if there are already k or more skills in the library with a simigreater than θ, where k = 2.",
    "For retrieving skills, the same SentenceBERT model is employed.",
    "When a subagent is assigned a new subtask, the model finds the top k most relevant skills by comparing the embeddings of the subtask's name to those in the library.",
    "These skills are then provided to the subagent in textual form, aiding in the execution of the task."
  ],
